data.description: Move-in ready beautiful townhouse in a great East Charlotte location! Perfect for first-time home buyers looking for an affordable option or investors looking to add to their rental portfolio. This spacious home features an abundance of natural light, wood-burning fireplace, beautiful kitchen w/crisp white cabinets, subway tile backsplash and SS appliances, LVP flooring on the main level, private fenced-in front and back patios, perfect for entertaining. The upper level features a large primary bedroom w/walk-in closet and a private terrace, perfect for relaxing while enjoying a cup of coffee or glass of wine; spacious secondary bedrooms w/walk-in closets, updated full bathroom w/tub, and linen closet.  The Four Seasons Community offers a clubhouse, outdoor pool and playground. Amazing location - minutes to uptown Charlotte, shops, restaurants, entertainment, hospitals, public transportation, major highways and everything you will ever need! Don't miss out on this great opportunity!
